Title: They're So Thorny!
Description:
The crate, once full of desperately needed supplies, has been thoroughly pillaged.

A quick scan of the area shows evidence left behind by the thieves. Icy thorns, just like the ones on the water sprites on the shoreline to the east.

This is a life or death situation for your band of survivors. Those supplies need to be retrieved from these thieving pests and returned to camp.
ObjectivesText: Collect 5 Emergency Supplies from the Water Sprites.
